abstract: Church van runs stop sign in southwest Florida, crossing all four lanes of highway and crashing into canal, killing eight people and injuring 10.
lead_paragraph: Ten others were injured when the vehicle ran through a stop sign, crossed all lanes of a highway and landed in a canal.

headline.main: Crash of Church Van Kills 8 in Rural Florida
headline.print_headline: National Briefing | South; Florida: Eight Are Killed in Van Crash
